          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Shared Auth and Telemetry Libraries"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "When 40 Claude services each implement JWT validation and OpenTelemetry setup independently, a single breaking change to the identity provider or a missed security patch requires 40 separate fixes. "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Shared libraries",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " for authentication and telemetry centralize these concerns: a single fix in "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "acme-auth",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " or "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "acme-telemetry",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " propagates to the entire fleet via a version bump."
          }
        ]
      },
